*Svemir* je neizmerno veliko mesto. (The universe is an infinitely large place.)

On je znao da će se jednog dana suočiti sa *svemirom*. (He knew that one day he would face the universe.)

Kosmonauti su obišli veliki deo *svemira*. (Cosmonauts have traveled a great deal of the universe.)

Naučnici i dalje otkrivaju nove činjenice o *svemiru*. (Scientists are still discovering new facts about the universe.)

Ova planeta je samo mali deo *svemira*. (This planet is just a small part of the universe.)